lumis.portal.monitor

Interface IEvent


  • @StableMinor(version="8.1",
             sinceVersion="4.1")
public interface IEvent
    An event that may be monitored. Its definition specifies how its data is collected and aggregated.
    Since:
    4.1.0
    Version:
    $Revision: 17593 $ $Date: 2015-07-17 11:21:36 -0300 (Fri, 17 Jul 2015) $
    See Also:
    lumis.portal.monitor
